data.description: Welcome home!!! (FHA loan is assumable at 4.5% - Loan approximately $297K) Enter through the front door into a gigantic front living room with a large open concept, tall ceilings, and a kitchen island big enough to get stranded on. Granite counters gleam, and a deep kitchen sink adjacent to a huge walk-in pantry. Continue down the hallway to 2 bedrooms separated by an additional den/living area with access to the covered rear patio. The primary bedroom features a large foot print and easy access to the massive bathroom and walk-in closet built for royalty. A secret cabinet is also installed in the closet to easily pass dirty clothes from the closet to the laundry room. This is a must-see home in a highly desirable HOA with loads of community facilities. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!!
